<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4616903>
    dc:description "Figs 5–8. Libnotes (Libnotes) pseudonohirai sp. nov. 5. Habitus of male adult, lateral view. 6. Thorax, dorsal view. 7. Hypopygium, ventral view. 8. Hypopygium, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1=5.0 mm, 2=1.0mm, 3–4=0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4616903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4616901>
    dc:description "Figs 1–4. Libnotes (Libnotes) wanensis sp. nov. 1. Habitus of male adult, lateral view. 2. Thorax, dorsal view. 3. Hypopygium, ventral view. 4. Hypopygium, dorsal view. Abbreviations: aa, anterior arculus; aed, aedeagus; goncx, gonocoxite; i gonst, inner gonostylus; o gonst, outer gonostylus; pm, paramere. Scale bars: 1=5.0 mm, 2=1.0mm, 3–4 =0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4616901/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

